# 30th Army Corps (Russian Empire)

|allegiance=Imperial Russian Army
|battles = World War I
}}
The 30th Army Corps was an Army corps in the Imperial Russian Army.
Part of
*11th Army: 1914 - 1915
*9th Army: 1915
*8th Army: 1915 - 1916
*Russian Special Army: 1916
*4th Army: 1916 - 1917
Commanders
*1915-1916: Andrei Zayonchkovski
